data.description: Taking Backups the phrase 'CURRENTLY UNDER CONTRACT, SELLER WILL CONSIDER BACKUP OFFERS' Welcome to this gorgeous southern charmer located in Tapestry Park community. This home is one of the best priced custom homes per square foot on Panama City Beach!  This is a well maintained 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath with wonderful open floor plan.  The 1st floor features a spacious great room with engineered wood flooring, high ceilings and built in bookshelves. Just off the great room, is the dining & kitchen area.  The kitchen has plenty of cabinetry space- soft closing drawers, plus pantry, and equipped with all Stainless kitchen appliances. The Master bedroom is also located on the first level. It features one large walk-in closet and a secondary closet. The master bath features double vanity, plus a makeup vanity, separate shower, and whirlpool tub.  Also on the first level is a guest bedroom, or flex room that can be utilized as a home office.Upstairs features 2 bedrooms, with a split floor-plan divided by large landing area overlooking the great room. Plus, a full bathroom featuring a double vanity and makeup vanity. The home has a large screened in back porch. The backyard has a fire pit and is enclosed with vinyl fencing.   Oversized 23x27 garage with plenty of space for vehicles, workbench, and storage.     The home has Tankless Rinnai water heater. The HVAC systems were replaced in 2019. NEW Carpet in all the bedrooms.  Both the interior walls and exterior siding has been recently painted.  The neighborhood includes AMENITIES too.  Clubhouse, 2 community swimming pools, tennis court, basketball court, and a  playground.  The  neighborhood also has unground utilities and sidewalks,  It close to dining, shopping, schools, and several other recreation activities including only being a few blocks to the white sandy beaches of the emerald coast.  Currently has a VA Assumable loan.  Schedule a tour today!
